{
  "page": "Sea Demons: A History of the Children of the Drowned God of the Isles",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Sea Demons: A History of the Children of the Drowned God of the Isles</b></i> is a work written by <a href=\"/index.php/Archmaester\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Archmaester\">Archmaester</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Mancaster\" title=\"Mancaster\">Mancaster</a>, concerning the history of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a>. Archmaester <a href=\"/index.php/Gyldayn\" title=\"Gyldayn\">Gyldayn</a> finds the chapters about the conflict between <a href=\"/index.php/Dalton_Greyjoy\" title=\"Dalton Greyjoy\">Dalton Greyjoy</a>'s Ironborn and the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a> to be especially good.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Contents\">Contents</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sea_Demons:_A_History_of_the_Children_of_the_Drowned_God_of_the_Isles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Contents\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>This book describes the history of the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a>, including the details of the war between <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">Ironborn</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Westerlands\" title=\"Westerlands\">Westerlands</a> covering from the end of the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a> and the beginning of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>'s <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sea_Demons:_A_History_of_the_Children_of_the_Drowned_God_of_the_Isles&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_the_hooded_hand.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - The Hooded Hand.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260405001838\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.011 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.012 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 217/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8588/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 793/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 368/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1037/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time repo